ED_Title: Implementation of the resolutions of the United Nations
ED_DecisionText:
At its 96th plenary meeting on 8 September 2017, the General Assembly decided to include the item entitled “Implementation of the resolutions of the United Nations” in the draft agenda of its seventy-second session.

(See A/71/PV.96)
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of this decision will be contained in document A/71/49 (Vol. III) after editorial review.
